      Boolean getChangedDuringCheckout()
      * true = the customer made changes to their account during this checkout * false = the customer didn't change anything to their account during this checkout/n The changes ment here are changes to billing & shipping address details, new payment account (tokens), or new users(s) added.

      The date (YYYYMMDD) on which the customer created their account with you
